title: Extract Image features from pretrained NN
description: In this kernel I want to demonstrate how to extract features from the pet images using a pretrained network. Since there are often none or multiple images of different resoltuions and aspect ratio I make the following preprocessing steps:  Take only profile picture (if existing else black) pad to square aspect ratio resize to 256
